      <title>中国特使就台湾选举言论斥责澳大利亚</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-s-envoy-rebukes-australia-over-taiwan-election-comment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国就外交部在堪培拉就台湾选举结果发表的声明向澳大利亚提出“严正交涉”，这是对最近改善的两国关系的最新挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-s-envoy-rebukes-australia-over-taiwan-election-comment</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 06:04:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科索沃将部署美国新型反坦克武器，塞尔维亚感到愤怒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/kosovo-to-deploy-new-us-anti-tank-weapons-as-serbia-bristles</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科索沃国防部长表示，在该国北部发生暴力冲突、与塞尔维亚的紧张局势急剧升级四个月后，美国提供的反坦克导弹的涌入将更好地保卫这个巴尔干国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/kosovo-to-deploy-new-us-anti-tank-weapons-as-serbia-bristles</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 06:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯危机后，欧盟帮助摩尔多瓦通胀崩溃</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/inflation-collapse-in-moldova-helped-by-eu-after-russia-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩尔多瓦央行行长表示，通货膨胀的暴跌表明，随着摩尔多瓦夹在乌克兰和罗马尼亚之间寻求加入欧盟，突然放弃俄罗斯能源已经得到了回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/inflation-collapse-in-moldova-helped-by-eu-after-russia-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 05:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着新罕布什尔州临近，德桑蒂斯试图摆脱特朗普获胜的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/desantis-tries-to-shrug-off-trump-win-as-new-hampshire-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离关键的新罕布什尔州初选还有一周，罗恩·德桑蒂斯试图正确看待唐纳德·特朗普在爱荷华州党团会议上取得的压倒性胜利，因为他正在为留在共和党总统竞选中而奋斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/desantis-tries-to-shrug-off-trump-win-as-new-hampshire-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 04:35:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普追查白宫与法尼·威利斯律师之间的记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/trump-goes-after-records-between-white-house-fani-willis-lawyer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前总统唐纳德·特朗普要求提供记录，他称这些记录可能显示拜登政府与佐治亚州检察官之间就针对他干预选举的指控进行协调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/trump-goes-after-records-between-white-house-fani-willis-lawyer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 03:41:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>台湾突然改变报道中国军事活动的方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/taiwan-abruptly-changes-how-it-reports-china-military-activities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾在选出一位亲美总统几天后改变了报道中国在台湾地区军事活动的方式，北京称这位总统为“战争煽动者”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/taiwan-abruptly-changes-how-it-reports-china-military-activities</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 02:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国新冠死亡人数和低出生人数创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-population-extends-historic-decline-as-covid-deaths-surged</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2023年，随着出生率降至历史新低，中国人口下降速度加快，加速了人口结构的转变，这对已经在应对通货紧缩压力和房地产危机的政府构成了长期挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/china-population-extends-historic-decline-as-covid-deaths-surged</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 02:09:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普寻求通过市场言论重塑对华强硬形象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/trump-says-china-markets-crashed-on-iowa-caucus-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将再次将对中国的立场作为其美国总统竞选策略的关键部分，并在美国股市的动荡与他在爱荷华州共和党党团会议上的失控胜利之间建立了未经证实的关联。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/trump-says-china-markets-crashed-on-iowa-caucus-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 02:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦称伊朗在紧张局势蔓延时发动了致命袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/pakistan-condemns-iran-over-deadly-strike-inside-its-territory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦谴责伊朗对其领土进行明显的导弹袭击，在地区动荡之际引发了德黑兰与其核武器邻国之间的外交危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-17/pakistan-condemns-iran-over-deadly-strike-inside-its-territory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 01:14:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>参议员梅嫩德斯和他的妻子寻求对贿赂指控进行单独审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/senator-menendez-wife-seek-separate-trials-on-bribery-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国参议员鲍勃·梅南德斯 (Bob Menendez) 和他的妻子因贿赂指控而被一起起诉，他们各自要求法官进行单独审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-16/senator-menendez-wife-seek-separate-trials-on-bribery-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2024 13:42:58 GMT</pubDate>
